                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="what-is-the-purpose-of-narrative-text">
                            1. WHAT IS THE PURPOSE OF NARRATIVE TEXT</h2><br />
                        to amuse/entertain the readers1.to entertain the reader<br />2.to give us a moral value<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="what-is-the-purpose-of-narrative-text%e2%80%8b">
                            2. What is the purpose of narrative text?​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>The purpose of narrative text is to entertain the reader or present a story.</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>The purpose of narrative text is to entertain the reader or present a story. For example, a fairy tale is a narrative text structure. Narrative text structures should be easy to remember because the structure follows a story with a beginning, a middle, and an end.</p><br />
